data.description: This immaculate 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is a true gem. As you enter through the foyer, you'll immediately notice the thoughtfully designed layout. The kitchen, situated to your right, is a culinary enthusiast's dream. It boasts an abundance of cabinets, an inviting eat-in area, a convenient island with seating, an elegant backsplash, a pantry for storage, and exquisite crown molding.    The master suite is a tranquil retreat with its own walk-in closet, providing ample space for your wardrobe. The master bathroom is equally impressive, featuring dual sinks, a separate shower, and a luxurious garden tub – perfect for unwinding after a long day.    Step onto the screened-in patio, where you can relax comfortably while enjoying the outdoors. A cooling fan adds to your comfort, making it an ideal spot to unwind. The spacious backyard offers exciting possibilities, whether you envision a pool for those hot summer days or a flourishing garden.    This home is nestled in a community that truly caters to your lifestyle. Enjoy a game of tennis, watch your little ones play at the playground, or make use of the clubhouse for gatherings. And when it's time to beat the heat, you have not one, but two swimming pools to choose from. Whether you're looking to swim laps or enjoy family time, these pools have you covered. With exciting features like slides and a walk-in area, everyone can have a great time. And for those who appreciate golf, the added bonus of a golf course within the community completes the picture.    Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity. Contact us today to schedule your appointment and experience all that this home and community have to offer.
